  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "The second script collection prints the production texts behind six further Horus Heresy audio dramas, with editor Laurie Goulding's introduction, soundtrack cues, and character notes. Malcador the Sigillite shapes a quiet war on Terra in 'The Sigillite.' Captain Garro returns three times — 'Sword of Truth' and 'Burden of Duty' continue his Knight-Errant arc, while 'Honour to the Dead' tracks a haunted Death Guard frigate. 'Grey Angel' sends an Inquisitor and a Knight-Errant chasing rumours of one of the Lion's sons. 'Censure' drops Aeonid Thiel and a handful of Ultramarines onto a fractured world to hunt a Word Bearers preacher dug in among the rubble. A reference volume for listeners who want the page behind the audio.",
